Package: GTestimate
Title: Estimating scRNA-seq gene expression using the Good-Turing estimator
Version: 0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Martin", "Fahrenberger", , "martin.fahrenberger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1107-0197"))
Description: GTestimate provides easy to use Good Turing estimation for the per cell gene expression values from scRNA-seq experiment. By using the Good Tuing estimator it accounts for the probability that the next hypothetical sequencing read would be of a previously unobserved gene.
